'''圓尾鱟'''（[[学名|学名]]：''{{lang|la|Carcinoscorpius rotundicauda}}''），也叫'''馬蹄蟹'''或'''鱟'''，是[[世界自然基金會|世界自然基金會]]“海洋十寶”之一，也是現存鱟類中個體最小的一种。圓尾鱟有毒<ref>{{cite news|author1=晓石|author2=应红燕|author3=俞莹|title=把它当中国鲎吃宁波6人差点丢性命·都市快报|url=http://hzdaily.hangzhou.com.cn/dskb/html/2014-06/16/content_1746117.htm|accessdate=2017-03-20|work=hzdaily.hangzhou.com.cn|agency=都市快报|issue=5638<!--原圖片http://hzdaily.hangzhou.com.cn/dskb/page/3/2014-06/16/01/2014061601_brief.jpg看不清楚，https://zh.wikipedia.org/w/index.php?title=Wikipedia:沙盒&oldid=43693111這樣子算出來的。。-->|publisher=都市快报|date=2014-06-16|archive-date=2018-08-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180806054645/http://hzdaily.hangzhou.com.cn/dskb/html/2014-06/16/content_1746117.htm|dead-url=no}}[https://www.zhihu.com/question/40417987 为什么这么多人分不清圆尾鲎和中华鲎的区别？ - 知乎] {{Wayback|url=https://www.zhihu.com/question/40417987 |date=20170321081503 }}</ref>。

雖然被稱為馬蹄蟹，不過圓尾鱟實際上比起[[螃蟹|螃蟹]]，與[[蜘蛛|蜘蛛]]和[[蠍子|蠍子]]擁有更近的親緣關係（同屬於[[螯肢亞門|螯肢亞門]]）。圓尾鱟的名稱緣由來自於其尾部（[[尾節|尾節]]）截面為圓形，其他種類的鱟尾部則皆為三角形<ref name=AboutTheSpecies>{{cite web | url=http://www.horseshoecrab.org/nh/species.html | title=About the Species | publisher=The Horseshoe Crab | accessdate=2018-06-26 | archive-date=2007-02-12 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20070212205702/http://www.horseshoecrab.org/nh/species.html | dead-url=no }}</ref>。

== 分佈 ==
[[File:Mangrove_Horseshoe_Crab_(Carcinoscorpius_rotundicauda)_(6707310189).jpg|thumb]]的圓尾鱟]]
見於[[印度|印度]]、[[孟加拉|孟加拉]]、[[印尼|印尼]]、[[馬來西亞|馬來西亞]]、[[新加坡|新加坡]]、[[泰國|泰國]]、[[柬埔寨|柬埔寨]]、[[緬甸|緬甸]]、[[中國|中國]]與[[香港|香港]]沿海與[[汽水_(水域)|汽水]]地區<ref name=Vestbo2018>{{cite journal| author1=Stine Vestbo | author2=Matthias Obst | author3=Francisco J. Quevedo Fernandez | author4=Itsara Intanai | author5=Peter Funch | year=2018 | title=Present and Potential Future Distributions of Asian Horseshoe Crabs Determine Areas for Conservation | journal=Frontiers in Marine Science | volume=5 | issue=164 | page=1-16 | doi=10.3389/fmars.2018.00164 }}</ref>。成年圓尾鱟多見於深水，而幼鱟多見於潮間帶淺水區。

== 繁殖行為 ==
潮間帶沙灘和泥灘是牠們的繁殖地。圓尾鱟會於[[滿月|滿月]]與[[新月|新月]]水漲時到聚集至沙泥灘，圓尾鱟採[[單配偶制|單配偶制]]，雄鱟會透過[[螯肢|螯肢]]攀附在雌鱟身上直到雌鱟產卵，每隻雌性每次約產下二千枚卵，雄性會在雌性產卵後進行[[體外受精|體外受精]]。但由於圓尾鱟在野外的存活率偏低，在一萬隻幼鱟中，大約只有1到2只可存活10到15年。

新加坡的圓尾鱟繁殖期為四月至八月，每次{{link-en|蛻皮|Moulting}}後幼體的體型能增加33%，經歷五次蛻皮後幼體就會從{{convert|2|cm}}成長至成年體長<ref>{{cite journal |author1=Lesley Cartwright-Taylor |author2=Julian Lee |author3=Chia Chi Hsu |lastauthoramp=yes |year=2009 |title=Population structure and breeding pattern of the mangrove horseshoe crab ''Carcinoscorpius rotundicauda'' in Singapore |journal=[[Aquatic_Biology|Aquatic Biology]] |volume=8 |pages=61–69 |url=http://www.int-res.com/abstracts/ab/v8/n1/p61-69/ |doi=10.3354/ab00206 |access-date=2018-07-21 |archive-date=2020-11-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201111222301/https://www.int-res.com/abstracts/ab/v8/n1/p61-69 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

== 食物 ==
圓尾鱟為[[底棲生物|底棲生物]]，主要以[[沙蟲|沙蟲]]、蠕蟲、小[[蟹|蟹]]、[[蠔|蠔]]和[[貽貝|貽貝]]的雙殼類動物為食<ref name="Zhou">{{cite journal |author1=H. Zhou  |author2=Brian Morton  |lastauthoramp=yes |year=2004 |title=The diets of juvenile horseshoe crabs, ''Tachypleus tridentatus'' and ''Carcinoscorpius rotundicauda'' (Xiphosura), from nursery beaches proposed for conservation in Hong Kong |journal=[[Journal_of_Natural_History|Journal of Natural History]] |volume=38 |issue=15 |pages=1915–1925 |doi=10.1080/0022293031000155377 }}</ref>。

== 与人類的關係 ==
[[File:Carcinoscorpius_rotundicauda_(Chonburi).jpg|thumb]]一桶捕捉到的圓尾鱟]]
[[File:Yam_Khai_Maengda-Cha_Am-4-13.JPG|thumb]]的鱟蛋沙拉“Yam Khai Maengda”]]
圓尾鱟受到過度捕捞，数量已銳減<ref name="Pati">{{cite news |author=Bibhuti Pati |date=2008-06-24 |title=Horseshoe crabs galloping towards extinction |publisher=[[Merinews|Merinews]] |url=http://www.merinews.com/article/horseshoe-crabs-galloping-towards-extinction/136265.shtml |accessdate=2011-06-01 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121005225450/http://www.merinews.com/article/horseshoe-crabs-galloping-towards-extinction/136265.shtml |archive-date=2012-10-05 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。但[[世界自然保護聯盟|世界自然保護聯盟]]紅色名錄把圓尾鱟列入“資料不足”部分。

圓尾鱟的肉並不多，但是其[[魚卵|卵]]多半會被視為珍饈<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://praneesthaikitchen.com/2013/01/28/horseshoe-crab-egg-salad-recipe/ |title=存档副本 |accessdate=2018-07-21 |archive-date=2020-10-30 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201030130445/https://praneesthaikitchen.com/2013/01/28/horseshoe-crab-egg-salad-recipe/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>，圓尾鱟其實有毒性<ref>{{cite journal |vauthors=Ngy L, Yu CF, Takatani T, Arakawa O |title=Toxicity assessment for the horseshoe crab Carcinoscorpius rotundicauda collected from Cambodia |url=https://archive.org/details/sim_toxicon_2007-05_49_6/page/843 |journal=Toxicon |volume=49 |issue=6 |pages=843–7 |date=May 2007  |pmid=17261323 |doi=10.1016/j.toxicon.2006.12.004}}</ref>，與其他鱟不同，圓尾鱟含有足以使人類致命的[[河魨毒素|河魨毒素]]<ref>{{Cite journal|last=Kanchanapongkul|first=J.|last2=Krittayapoositpot|first2=P.|date=June 1995|title=An epidemic of tetrodotoxin poisoning following ingestion of the horseshoe crab Carcinoscorpius rotundicauda|journal=The Southeast Asian Journal of Tropical Medicine and Public Health|volume=26|issue=2|pages=364–367|issn=0125-1562|pmid=8629077}}</ref>。生物學上，其藍色的血可用來緩解精神疲劳以及治療[[腸胃炎|腸胃炎]]。它們的血液還可以做成[[鲎试剂|鲎试剂]]來進行内[[病原體|病原體]][[脂多糖|脂多糖]]检测<ref name="Pati"/>。

